metadata.title: CalCOFI Temperature, Salinity and Nutrient Profiles (US-California)

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Environmental Satellite, Data
Information Service (NESDIS), National Oceanographic Data Center (NODC)

metadata.description:
Water column profiles from water bottles, C/STD measurements

CALCOFI (California Current Region), coastal California, ex: 28-29N Lat, 114-115W long

Publication
Data reports - Physical and Chemical Data, CALCOFI Cruise 6901, 7-30 January 1969 and CALCOFI cruise 6902, January 11- March 1969 (SIO Reference 76-14, Sept 1976 (313006) NOAA/WDCA 139.8 D-72:1976 Sep.

Data Distribution
Available as individual data sets or as part of the NODC Oceanographic Station Profile Time Series CD ROM (CALCOFI 1 & 2).  Also included in WOA 1994

URL -- ( http://www.nodc.noaa.gov/General/CDR-detdesc/time-series.html )  
[ A TCODE project ]
